{"_path":"/_lood/betti-alver-kaks-saarlast","_dir":"_lood","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Kaks saarlast","description":"Kaks saarlast muiste ühte lõid, koos laulsid, riisusid ja jõid!","layout":"story-page","author":"Betti Alver","images":[{"src":"betti-alver-kaks-saarlast.webp"}],"tags":["sõprus","saarlane","laul","Suur Tõll","luule","tamm"],"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":""},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"binding","props":{"value":"$doc.title"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kaks saarlast muiste ühte lõid, koos laulsid, riisusid ja jõid – "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nüks, hiiglasuur ja äge, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nööd-päevad taprit kõhutas, hulljulgeid plaane õhutas "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja juhtis röövliväge. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKuid teisel oli lihtne meel, ta sulasena sõjateel "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nleent lõkketulel soendas "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja sõbra haavu loendas. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNii jäädi kokku, kuni pard neil valgeks mõlemal kui kard "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nläks heitluses ja ohus. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nSiis aga lõksu langeb salk ja saabub kurja elu palk: "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nneid surma mõistab kohus. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nSääl kajab jõugust juhi hüüd: “Ma üksi kannan veresüüd – "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nlas maksab minu ihu, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkuid säästa teiste lihu!” "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nJa kohtunik nii kalk ja noor, näost kaame nagu kasekoor, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ntal vastab pilke moega: "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n“Kui pääd sult nõuabki me viis, kas pääta ülem päästa siis "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nei saa mõnd mehepoega? "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKõik poisid rivistugu teel, ja kellest mööda joosta veel "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nsa pärast nuhtlust jõuad – "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\npriid olgu, nagu nõuad.” "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nNii jõuab kätte jube viiv, maas verest mustaks värvub liiv "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja vait jääb hirmund vägi. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nKuid hiiglamees – ennäe, ennäe! sääl tõstab ühe, teise käe "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nja kerkib maast kui mägi. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nJa kõmiseb ta raske samm, ja nagu tuules murduv tamm, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nmis järgneb maruhoole, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nta tormab meeste poole. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nHall saarlane on viimne reas, ja kisa tõuseb salga seas, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\net hirmus juht ei langeks. "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nVeel samm, veel samm, ja pääta mees on oma verevenna ees, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nkuid sulane jääb rangeks, "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nning hüüdes: “Ei! kui sured sa, siis elada ei taha ka "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nsu vana soldan mette!” – "},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\ntal pani jala ette."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"story-author","props":{":author":"author"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"details-wrapper","props":{"summary":"Mis mõtted tekkisid?"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ballaadi esitab näitleja Aarne Üksküla: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arhiiv.err.ee/vaata/15207","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://arhiiv.err.ee/vaata/15207"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Balladi sünniloo saad teada siit: (link taustaloole, kus Betti Alver räägib proua Talvikuga)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mida tähendab sinu jaoks sõprus? Milles see väljendub, et keegi on su sõber ehk millist inimest nimetad oma sõbraks?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kuidas leidsid oma kõige esimese sõbra? Kas olete sõbrad siiani?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Kui suur osa su suhtlusest sõpradega toimub sotsiaalmeedias ja kui suur osa vahetult, näost-näkku?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mida sa sõpradega koos teed?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mis sa arvad, kas sõpru leitakse kogu elu jooksul või pigem mingil elu perioodil, nt lapsepõlves ja koolieas? Millest see sõltub?"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"details-wrapper","props":{"summary":"Allikad","className":["text-sm"],"icon":"icon-park-outline:document-folder"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ballaad: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Betti Alver"}]},{"type":"text","value":", “Kaks saarlast” (1939), luulekogu “Tähetund”, Eesti Raamat, Tallinn, 1966."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Betti Alveri elu ja loomingu kohta saab lugeda siit: "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://kultuur.err.ee/1608314084/onnepalu-betti-alveri-luule-ei-puua-olla-sugav-vaid-on-seda-enese-tahtmata","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://kultuur.err.ee/1608314084/onnepalu-betti-alveri-luule-ei-puua-olla-sugav-vaid-on-seda-enese-tahtmata"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Foto: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Merit Karise"}]}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:_lood:betti-alver-kaks-saarlast.md","_source":"content","_file":"_lood/betti-alver-kaks-saarlast.md","_extension":"md"}